title: RHOBH: The Wrath of Kath
itunes:title: RHOBH: The Wrath of Kath
description:
The Aspen trip comes to a close and we finally get (some) answers about what happened with Kath, although more questions are also posed, like why didn't Mo know Kath was raging? Did Rick get involved? What shoes did Kath use to stomp the glasses?? These questions and more are explored in this Real Housewives of Beverly Hills recap!
